    • net.sf.jguiraffe.di.impl.TestSetPropertyInvocation

  • public class TestSetPropertyInvocation
extends Object
    Test class for SetPropertyInvocation. Note that this class cannot be derived from AbstractInvocationTest because some of the default properties of invocations are treated differently by this class.
